Fireworks go off during the closing ceremony at the Russia-hosted 2020 International Army Games at the Alabino training ground, near Moscow on Saturday. More than 5,000 participants from 156 teams from over 30 countries and regions competed in the games. Over 260 contestants from six Chinese teams participated in six competitions, including the tank biathlon. Photo: VCG  
